</div>NO offense but that is really a dumb line of thinking.  Pouncey is clearly the #1 guy at his position, a position he would have been #1 in last year and would be #1 in next year.  Troy was NEVER #1 at ANYTHING (maybe in little gridders).  Pouncey may go in the top 15 and you think we should wait and see if he's there in the 2nd?  give me a break.</div>
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div><br />
